{"type":"message","id":"b0291f60","parentId":"99a52726","timestamp":"2026-02-21T01:10:04.049Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_phi1x08jakcu_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>A股开盘前资讯</title>\n    <style>\n        body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif; background: #f5f5f5; margin: 0; padding: 20px; }\n        .container { max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; background: #fff; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }\n        .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a73e8, #4285f4); color: white; padding: 30px; text-align: center; }\n        .header h1 { margin: 0; font-size: 28px; }\n        .header p { margin: 10px 0 0; opacity: 0.9; font-size: 14px; }\n        .section { padding: 24px; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; }\n        .section:last-child { border-bottom: none; }\n        .section-title { font-size: 20px; font-weight: 600; color: #1a73e8; margin: 0 0 16px 0; display: flex; align-items: center; }\n        .section-title::before { content: ''; display: inline-block; width: 4px; height: 20px; background: #1a73e8; border-radius: 2px; margin-right: 10px; }\n        .news-item { padding: 12px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0; }\n        .news-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }\n        .news-title { font-size: 15px; color: #333; margin: 0 0 6px 0; line-height: 1.5; }\n        .news-title a { color: #1a73e8; text-decoration: none; }\n        .news-title a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }\n        .news-meta { font-size: 12px; color: #888; }\n        .tag { display: inline-block; padding: 2px 8px; background: #e8f0fe; color: #1a73e8; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 11px; margin-right: 8px; }\n        .tag-hot { background: #ffe0e0; color: #d93025; }\n        .footer { background: #f8f8f8; padding: 20px; text-align: center; color: #666; font-size: 12px; }\n        .source-tag { display: inline-block; padding: 2px 6px; background: #e0e0e0; color: #666; border-radius: 3px; font-size: 10px; margin-right: 8px; }\n        .source-yicai { background: #ff6b6b; color: white; }\n        .source-eastmoney { background: #4ecdc4; color: white; }\n        .source-163 { background: #ff9f43; color: white; }\n        .source-sina { background: #ee5a24; color: white; }\n        .source-10jqka { background: #00d2d3; color: white; }\n        .section-header { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; }\n        .news-count { font-size: 12px; color: #888; font-weight: normal; }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"header\">\n            <h1>📈 A股开盘前资讯</h1>\n            <p>2026年2月19日 · 星期三</p>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"section\">\n            <div class=\"section-header\">\n                <h2 class=\"section-title\">🤖 机器人板块 <span class=\"news-count\">(TOP 20)</span></h2>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <h3 class=\"news-title\">宇树机器人马年秀出\"赛博真功夫\"，突破运动性能极限</h3>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-yicai\">第一财经</span>2026-02-17</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <h3 class=\"news-title\">魔法原子机器人\"霸屏\"春晚，具身智能资本风向生变</h3>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-163\">网易财经</span>2026-02-18</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <h3 class=\"news-title\">这个春节999元租个人形机器人拜年，然后呢？</h3>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-163\">网易财经</span>2026-02-18</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <h3 class=\"news-title\">当春晚进入智能科技周期，追觅站上C位</h3>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-163\">网易财经</span>2026-02-18</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <h3 class=\"news-title\">不止有机器人！这抹\"中国红\"也是春晚的隐藏主角</h3>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-163\">网易财经</span>2026-02-18</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <h3 class=\"news-title\">中大型无人机首次集群亮相春晚，还有这些低空飞行器登场</h3>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-yicai\">第一财经</span>2026-02-17</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <h3 class=\"news-title\">宇树科技王兴兴：今年宇树科技的目标出货量在1-2万台左右</h3>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-163\">网易财经</span>2026-02-18</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <h3 class=\"news-title\">亿元\"入场券\"背后的暗战：机器人企业为何砸重金拼春晚？</h3>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-163\">网易财经</span>2026-02-18</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <h3 class=\"news-title\">两个春节，一年时间：战火烧红整条AI产业链</h3>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-yicai\">第一财经</span>2026-02-18</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <h3 class=\"news-title\">逆袭的变压器，又一个被AI搞火的\"老物件\"</h3>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-163\">网易财经</span>2026-02-18</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <h3 class=\"news-title\">性能持平价格大降80%，Anthropic新模型杀疯了</h3>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-163\">网易财经</span>2026-02-18</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <h3 class=\"news-title\">怡园酒业营收增长难阻股价探底</h3>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-163\">网易财经</span>2026-02-18</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <h3 class=\"news-title\">芯天下港股IPO：主营产品毛利率低于同行</h3>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-163\">网易财经</span>2026-02-18</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <h3 class=\"news-title\">岚图汽车港股上市最新进展：已获得全部前置监管审批</h3>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-163\">网易财经</span>2026-02-18</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <h3 class=\"news-title\"><a href=\"https://www.163.com/dy/article/KM2HQP310519875F.html\" target=\"_text\">AI红包爆卖50万个！24岁电商老板靠\"季节嗅觉\"年销1.2亿</h3>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-163\">网易财经</span>2026-02-18</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <h3 class=\"news-title\">业绩激增1000%，光芯片巨头，进击AI！</h3>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-163\">网易财经</span>2026-02-18</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <h3 class=\"news-title\">银河通用机器人：春晚上\"小盖\"的动作都不是提前编写程序的\"表演\"</h3>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-yicai\">第一财经</span>2026-02-17</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <h3 class=\"news-title\">史上最AI春晚！机器人组团抢C位 大厂\"撒红包\"竞逐AI流量入口</h3>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-yicai\">第一财经</span>2026-02-17</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <h3 class=\"news-title\">宇树科技春晚节目技术难点解析</h3>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-yicai\">第一财经</span>2026-02-17</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <h3 class=\"news-title\">印度举办AI\"影响力\"峰会，号称\"有史以来规模最大\"</h3>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-yicai\">第一财经</span>2026-02-17</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <h3 class=\"news-title\">豆包：除夕豆包AI互动总数达19亿</h3>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-yicai\">第一财经</span>2026-02-17</div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"section\">\n            <div class=\"section-header\">\n                <h2 class=\"section-title\">🧠 人工智能板块 <span class=\"news-count\">(TOP 20)</span></h2>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <h3 class=\"news-title\">AI进化速递 | 马斯克官宣Grok 4.2公测版上线</h3>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-yicai\">第一财经</span><span class=\"tag tag-hot\">热门</span>2026-02-18</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <h3 class=\"news-title\">宇树机器人刷新多个全球第一次</h3>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-yicai\">第一财经</span>2026-02-17</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <h3 class=\"news-title\">费城半导体指数上涨1.9%</h3>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-eastmoney\">东方财富</span>2026-02-18</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <h3 class=\"news-title\">谷歌推出Pixel10a智能手机</h3>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-eastmoney\">东方财富</span>2026-02-18</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <h3 class=\"news-title\">沙特Humain公司向xAI公司投资30亿美元</h3>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-eastmoney\">东方财富</span>2026-02-18</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <h3 class=\"news-title\">高通承诺为印度的战略人工智能风险投资基金出资高达1.5亿美元</h3>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-eastmoney\">东方财富</span>2026-02-18</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <h3 class=\"news-title\">英伟达美股盘前涨超2%</h3>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-eastmoney\">东方财富</span>2026-02-18</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <h3 class=\"news-title\">美股高开高走</h3>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-eastmoney\">东方财富</span>2026-02-18</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <h3 class=\"news-title\">全球市场：美股三大指数小幅收涨 苹果涨超3%</h3>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-eastmoney\">东方财富</span>2026-02-18</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <h3 class=\"news-title\">谷歌母公司Alphabet：印度政府与谷歌DeepMind建立合作伙伴关系</h3>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-eastmoney\">东方财富</span>2026-02-18</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <h3 class=\"news-title\">美股反弹，苹果涨超3%，标普500始终难上7000点</h3>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-yicai\">第一财经</span>2026-02-18</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <h3 class=\"news-title\">印度首次举办超大规模AI峰会，25万人将涌入</h3>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-yicai\">第一财经</span>2026-02-17</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <h3 class=\"news-title\">抖音集团李亮：炒作\"字节是恒科的最大空头\"很荒唐</h3>\n                <