{"type":"message","id":"d634568c","parentId":"a4e0c6f4","timestamp":"2026-02-21T01:16:31.062Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在让我测试一下msmtp是否可以发送邮件。","thinkingSignature":"2b8a5445487797557df8635c075fb3219ec960663ef0eed81cf76ad89ab3a69c"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_kjsrnjjsut5k_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat > /tmp/testmail.txt << 'EOF'\nTo: qn_home@163.com\nSubject: Test mail from msmtp\nContent-Type: text/html; charset=UTF-8\n\n<html><body><p>Test email</p></body></html>\nEOF\n\nmsmtp -t < /tmp/testmail.txt 2>&1"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":50189,"output":106,"cacheRead":8981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":59276,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1771636587436}}
{"type":"message","id":"35cc39c1","parentId":"d634568c","timestamp":"2026-02-21T01:16:31.654Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_kjsrnjjsut5k_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"msmtp: authentication failed (method PLAIN)\nmsmtp: server message: 550 User has no permission\nmsmtp: could not send mail (account default from /root/.msmtprc)\n\n(Command exited with code 77)"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":77,"durationMs":577,"aggregated":"msmtp: authentication failed (method PLAIN)\nmsmtp: server message: 550 User has no permission\nmsmtp: could not send mail (account default from /root/.msmtprc)\n\n(Command exited with code 77)","cwd":"/root/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1771636591643}}
{"type":"message","id":"e5adb38a","parentId":"35cc39c1","timestamp":"2026-02-21T01:16:36.081Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"认证失败。可能是授权码不正确或者需要使用不同的认证方法。让我检查一下163邮箱的SMTP设置。\n\n实际上，\"User has no permission\"这个错误通常意味着邮箱没有开启SMTP服务，或者授权码不正确。让我尝试使用一个不同的方法 - 也许可以尝试使用OAuth2或者检查授权码。\n\n让我先检查一下是否可以使用Python的其他邮件库来发送邮件。","thinkingSignature":"c0f0114b735a6a5056bde08371d3bb3c80837a32a2fb5b14b3daf020fce5b2fd"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_iwjlcrz39y20_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 -c \"import keyring; print(keyring.get_password('smtp', 'qn_home@163.com'))\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"No keyring\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":50359,"output":141,"cacheRead":8981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":59481,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1771636591654}}
